    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Gun Poker</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up poker night with Gun Poker, where your poker hand gives you a leg up in shooter action right on the table! Use your wits and your FPS skills to come out on top against 2-6 friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/3d6f0a92ad84ce136c3a482ea9d24d07.poster.avif?t=1761608487\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/3d6f0a92ad84ce136c3a482ea9d24d07.webm?t=1761608487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/3d6f0a92ad84ce136c3a482ea9d24d07.mp4?t=1761608487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play rapid-fire rounds of Texas Hold 'Em poker and FPS PvP until one player holds all the chips. Weigh the odds and raise the stakes when it counts to claim victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/5fb85a321aee50c4b6346fa2de9f6201.poster.avif?t=1761608487\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/5fb85a321aee50c4b6346fa2de9f6201.webm?t=1761608487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/5fb85a321aee50c4b6346fa2de9f6201.mp4?t=1761608487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Poker Hand Determines Your Gun</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A better hand will yield a better gun, but having the best gun on the field will not guarantee victory. Take advantage of grenades, dashing, and the chaotic environment to defeat an opponent with a stronger loadout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/faaa4f85fd709f81fec0c90d7cfabb05.poster.avif?t=1761608487\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/faaa4f85fd709f81fec0c90d7cfabb05.webm?t=1761608487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/faaa4f85fd709f81fec0c90d7cfabb05.mp4?t=1761608487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destructible Maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All maps are physically simulated. Use your grenades to topple card castles and domino structures to corner or smoke out your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/c98b7f5415264ff3a2234bd0f47d755d.poster.avif?t=1761608487\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/c98b7f5415264ff3a2234bd0f47d755d.webm?t=1761608487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056780/extras/c98b7f5415264ff3a2234bd0f47d755d.mp4?t=1761608487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Private or public lobbies up to 6 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 destructible maps and 4 background environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card and table skins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alternative and customizable decks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand cheat sheet for players new to poker</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Poker-only mode</p></li></ul>",
